command: from mazegen.types import Position, Maze, Solution; p = Position(row=0, col=1); assert p.row == 0 and p.col == 1; m = Maze(width=3, height=3, seed=42, start=Position(0,0), end=Position(2,2), passages=frozenset()); assert m.width == 3; s = Solution(found=True, path=(Position(0,0),)); assert s.found and len(s.path) == 1
